                        "description": "NUANSA 2024 presents a mesmerizing journey with \"Keong Mas: Daha to Surabaya,\" a reimagined tale blending ancient Javanese folklore with the pulse of modern Surabaya. In a unique twist, Candra Kirana finds herself displaced to present-day Surabaya, adding a new layer to her journey of self-discovery. NUANSA 2024 explores the timeless struggle of finding a home amidst the challenges of the modern world.",
