                        "description": "LUKISAN JATI (Portrait of Self) is a coming-of-age story about two aspiring artists - Raden Saleh, a pioneering painter and the first Indonesian scholar to study in Europe, and Elsa, a young present-day student who has won a prestigious scholarship to study art in Singapore. The glitz and glamour of city life sets the stage for Saleh and Elsa to chase their dreams of becoming successful artists, but with it comes challenges that will force them to question whether their art is worth pursuing.",
